* BrightBlade snarled, how dare he ignore her like that!           She had 
watched as Gangon had turned his back and walked away, she had stood there 
for nearly a day before her temper had calmed a bit
from his reaction.
She looked at the Maximal base and snarled at that as well, she never did 
like being shot by auto guns!
BrightBlade transformed into Beast Mode and began to make her way in the 
direction that Gangon had disappeared, she was steaming mad and wanted to 
take it out on somebot.
She looked behind her before walking away in the darkness, she thought death 
to anybot that crossed her path!!!*
